FBIS3-16516 "drsov052_t_94004" FBIS-SOV-94-052 Document Type:Daily Report 16 Mar 1994 BALTIC STATES Estonia Preparations for Dismantling Reactor Begin LD1603180194 Tallinn Radio Tallinn Network in Estonian 1600 GMT 16 Mar 94 LD1603180194 Tallinn Radio Tallinn Network Language: Estonian Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] Colonel Raul Luks, the commandant of Paldiski, has confirmed to the Estonian Telegraph Agency that everything is ready for the dismantlement of the nuclear reactor at the Paldiski training center. Estonian and Russian specialists met at Paldiski today to discuss cooperation for the period of the dismantlement. Luks said that they agreed about joint activity, the collection of initial information, and ways of cooperation. Luks could not answer a question on when the actual dismantlement of the reactor will begin. [passage omitted]
